{"tid":347941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港鐵故障：跪低要罰款　5粒鐘至少500萬元","createTime":"2017-08-05T09:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T11:39:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d64a77f7a3b45b6ad9e4d64e94656f10de8f911","tid":347941,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:12:45.000Z","msg":"港鐵觀塘線於今晨11時許發生故障，至今已逾5小時，服務仍未回復正常，今次事件相信會被罰款至少500萬港元。根據資料顯示，政府於2013年與港鐵公司完成票價調整機制檢討，當中引入服務表現安排。根據安排，港鐵發生31分鐘或以上因機件故障或人為因素導致的服務延誤事故，即會撥出款項，透過「即日第二程車費九折」優惠回饋乘客。<br />\n<br />\n根據服務表現安排就服務延誤所施加的罰款額如下： <br />\n<br />\n延誤31分鐘至1小時：罰100萬港元<br />\n延誤1至2小時：罰200萬港元<br />\n延誤2至3小時：罰300萬港元<br />\n延誤3至4小時：罰500萬港元<br />\n延誤逾4小時的每小時(或不足1小時)：罰250萬港元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170805/bkn-20170805163017261-0805_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170805%2Fbkn-20170805163017261-0805_00822_001.html&d=nQu%2BaJ7V9%2F1xxbMCRdAVA%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=151074d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170805/bkn-20170805163017261-0805_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f5101132f7ba6e4ba5c5ced8dbf1a6d70e678728","tid":347941,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"who pay?"},{"pid":"d1faed46e554b82dc8d8b14a3545219eb7e0893b","tid":347941,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>who pay?</blockquote><br />\nU lor"},{"pid":"1f512a61a86f3dbc754fa14a10605e50dbaf91fe","tid":347941,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>who pay?</blockquote><br />\nU lor</blockquote><br />\n失業，唔使搭佢"},{"pid":"d5437470782f27f8dec89430d4ab94d68c4acfb6","tid":347941,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>who pay?</blockquote><br />\n公帑"},{"pid":"4f21b99